  <summary date="2015-03-19T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Medicaid Parity Act of 2015

 Amends title XIX (Medicaid) of the Social Security Act to extend through 2019: (1) Medicaid payment parity with Medicare for primary care services furnished under the Medicaid program, and (2) the increased (to 100%) federal medical assistance percentage (FMAP, or federal matching rate) for additional payments for primary care services.</summary>
